# Dockerfile-specific ignore-file for the LEAN Rust AI Gateway build.
#
# BuildKit honors `<Dockerfile>.dockerignore` next to the Dockerfile and it takes
# precedence over the repo-root `.dockerignore`. The lean build only needs the
# rust workspace, so we ignore everything then re-include litellm-rust/ only.
*

# --- re-include the only build input ---
!litellm-rust/

# --- prune heavy / irrelevant subpaths back out ---
**/target/
**/.git/
.git/
**/.DS_Store
*.log
